Usage:
 * install django-sakkada
 * import CacheClearAdmin from sakkada.admin.clear_cache
 * set CacheClearAdmin as class of admin model
 * copy templates (admin/cache/*) to your application template folder
 * optionally set index_template attr in admin.site to show link at index page
   and replace {APP_NAME} and {MODEL_NAME} to real values

Example usage in Admin:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
from django.contrib import admin
from sakkada.admin.cache_clear import CacheClearAdmin

class SomeAdmin(CacheClearAdmin, admin.ModelAdmin):
    pass

# optionally set index_template attr
admin.site.index_template = 'admin/cache/index_admin.html'
